      "instruction": "<p>Deseed your <strong>pepper[s]</strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and chop into quarters</p><p>Peel and chop your <strong>shallot[s]</strong> into quarters</p><p>Crush your <strong>garlic clove[s]</strong> open with the side of a knife and remove the skin[s]</p><p>Cut your<strong> red chilli[es]</strong> in half lengthways, deseed (scrape the seeds out with a teaspoon) and chop roughly</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
