    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice your <strong>brioche bun[s]</strong> in half</p><p>Add the <strong>halved</strong> <strong>brioche</strong> to a large baking tray (or two) and put the tray in the oven for 3-4 min or until warmed through</p><p>Wash then remove 1<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span><strong>leaf </strong>from the<strong> lettuce</strong> per person, pat it dry with kitchen paper and set aside</p><p>Chop the<strong> inner core[s]</strong> into quarters, lengthways</p>",
